    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is paired with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains sharp, with a documented inspection of the rear subframe mounting points and refreshed rear trailing arm bushings (RTABs). While the exterior and interior show honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, providing a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension remains composed with OEM-spec dampers, ensuring the communicative steering feel this platform is known for. Recent fluid analysis and comprehensive service history available.",
      "price": 34500.0,
