      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 executive sedan is the perfect blend of luxury and dependable performance. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic silver that still holds a brilliant shine, showing only minor signs of careful use consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin has been kept in wonderful condition; the premium leather seats are supple and free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All onboard technology, including the navigation system, premium audio, and heated seats, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and efficiently, having benefited from a consistent schedule of synthetic oil changes and preventative maintenance. The suspension provides a smooth, rattle-free ride, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. With a clean title and a full set of service records included, this vehicle is ready for the road with no immediate work required.",
      "price": 34500.0,
